# Test API endpoints
# You can use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code

### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks

### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:3000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample Task",
  "description": "This is a sample task created via API",
  "assignee": "John Doe",
  "status": "pending"
}

### Search tasks by assignee
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/search?assignee=John Doe

### Search tasks by status
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/search?status=pending

### Search tasks by text
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/search/sample

### Update task status (replace {id} with actual task ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/tasks/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Delete task (replace {id} with actual task ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/tasks/{id}